I'm saved.

01:24:19.820 --> 01:24:22.820
Leave everything to me.

01:24:22.820 --> 01:24:27.900
Taste of my hyper-corrosive croutons, Archvillain.

01:24:27.900 --> 01:24:38.860
Hold on, buddy.

01:24:38.860 --> 01:24:40.860
You'll be free in a jiffy.

01:24:48.220 --> 01:24:51.220
But Powder Toastman, what about Muddy Mudskipper?

01:24:51.220 --> 01:24:52.220
Hmm.

01:24:52.220 --> 01:24:54.220
My gosh, you're right.

01:24:54.220 --> 01:24:56.220
How thoughtless of me.

01:24:56.220 --> 01:25:31.140
The intensity.

01:25:31.140 --> 01:25:33.140
Too strong.

01:25:33.140 --> 01:25:36.140
Quick man, cling tenaciously to my buttocks.

01:25:36.140 --> 01:25:38.140
Both of them?

01:25:38.140 --> 01:25:47.470
Another distress call.

01:25:47.470 --> 01:26:01.020
Yes?

01:26:01.020 --> 01:26:04.020
Leave everything to me.

01:26:04.020 --> 01:26:08.860
Listen, something's come up.

01:26:08.860 --> 01:26:17.950
Sorry, Mac, but I've got to attend to something really important.

01:26:19.950 --> 01:26:36.290
Hello, fellas.

01:26:36.290 --> 01:26:38.290
What seems to be the trouble?

01:26:38.290 --> 01:26:40.290
We are lucky, Powder Toast.

01:26:40.290 --> 01:26:43.290
Leave everything to me.

01:26:45.290 --> 01:27:29.490
I'm sorry, fellas.

01:27:29.490 --> 01:27:31.490
I almost forgot.

01:27:32.490 --> 01:28:03.000
My toast particles are dissipating.

01:28:03.000 --> 01:28:05.000
That can only mean one thing.

01:28:05.000 --> 01:28:08.000
A call from Washington.

01:28:19.900 --> 01:28:23.900
Mr. President, what seems to be the trouble?

01:28:24.900 --> 01:28:26.900
I've got it in my own zipper.

01:28:26.900 --> 01:28:31.520
Leave everything to me.

01:28:31.520 --> 01:28:45.970
Anytime you're ready, Mr. President.

01:28:45.970 --> 01:28:47.970
Okay, full.

01:28:52.360 --> 01:29:01.700
I'll thank you, Powder Toastman.

01:29:01.700 --> 01:29:04.700
And thus, the President goes into recovery.

01:29:04.700 --> 01:29:07.700
But what shall happen to America?

01:29:07.700 --> 01:29:10.700
Who will run the country?

01:29:10.700 --> 01:29:12.700
Leave everything to me.

01:29:12.700 --> 01:29:19.130
And Powder Toastman is sworn into office.

01:29:19.130 --> 01:29:23.130
I, Powder Toastman, do solemnly swear

01:29:23.130 --> 01:29:25.130
to relieve the American citizens

01:29:25.130 --> 01:29:28.130
of their basic human rights.

01:29:28.130 --> 01:29:38.100
Lovely assistants, take a letter.

01:29:38.100 --> 01:29:40.100
The letter M.

01:29:40.100 --> 01:29:43.100
Furthermore, let's hold off the talks with the Kremlin

01:29:43.100 --> 01:29:48.100
until we settle the new Three Stooges stamp controversy.

01:29:48.100 --> 01:29:51.100
Personally, my vote goes with Shemp.

01:29:51.100 --> 01:29:55.100
Although Curly is certainly nothing to take lightly.

01:29:55.100 --> 01:29:59.120
That'll be all, faithful one.

01:29:59.120 --> 01:30:03.120
Well, I guess that takes care of the day's business.

01:30:03.120 --> 01:30:06.120
Man, this job is too cushy for me.

01:30:08.120 --> 01:30:10.120
It's chilly in here.

01:30:10.120 --> 01:30:13.780
Here's the problem.

01:30:14.780 --> 01:30:16.780
The fire's died down.

01:30:17.780 --> 01:30:20.540
Let's see.

01:30:20.540 --> 01:30:26.010
Hmm, we need something dry here.

01:30:26.010 --> 01:30:28.010
Here's some dusty old papers.

01:30:30.010 --> 01:30:42.120
That's much better.

01:30:45.120 --> 01:31:07.180
What are you doing tomorrow evening?

01:31:07.180 --> 01:31:09.180
I'll watch some TV.

01:31:09.180 --> 01:31:11.180
It'll help me to relax.

01:31:11.180 --> 01:31:14.180
Watch Riding Stimpy as the Royal Canadian

01:31:14.180 --> 01:31:16.180
Tid Yaksman in a brand spanking new

01:31:16.180 --> 01:31:19.180
Red and Stimpy show at a special time.

01:31:19.180 --> 01:31:21.180
Tomorrow night at 7 o'clock,

01:31:21.180 --> 01:31:23.180
6 central only on Nick.

01:31:23.180 --> 01:31:44.940
Saturday night has arrived.

01:31:44.940 --> 01:31:47.940
And Saturday night belongs to Snick.

01:31:47.940 --> 01:31:57.070
My name's Heather and I'm playing Dorothy

01:31:57.070 --> 01:31:58.070
in the Wizard of Oz.

01:31:58.070 --> 01:31:59.070
This is Toto.

01:31:59.070 --> 01:32:00.070
Hi, Toto.

01:32:00.070 --> 01:32:01.070
Well, Toto's not a real dog,

01:32:01.070 --> 01:32:02.070
so if someone's over here,

01:32:02.070 --> 01:32:03.070
like trying to pat me on the arm,

01:32:03.070 --> 01:32:04.070
I'll have Toto here

01:32:04.070 --> 01:32:05.070
and he'll get hit in the head

01:32:05.070 --> 01:32:06.070
