01:32:06.070 --> 01:32:07.070
We're Toto.

01:32:07.070 --> 01:32:08.070
I bought my shoes

01:32:08.070 --> 01:32:10.070
and then they put glitter and sequins

01:32:10.070 --> 01:32:12.070
